    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>ffmpeg.party is committed to protecting your privacy. This page explains how the site handles your information.</p>

    <h2>Data collection</h2>
    <p>This is a static website hosted on GitHub Pages. The site does not collect, store, or process any personal information.</p>

    <h2>Local storage</h2>
    <p>Some tools use your browser's <code>localStorage</code> or <code>sessionStorage</code> to save form inputs for convenience. This data:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Stays on your device only</li>
      <li>Is never transmitted to any server</li>
      <li>Can be cleared at any time via your browser's data controls</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Third-party services</h2>
    <p>The site is hosted on GitHub Pages. See <a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-privacy-statement" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub's privacy statement</a> for their data practices.</p>

    <h2>Analytics</h2>
    <p>No analytics, no tracking, no cookies.</p>

    <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
    <p>This policy may be updated occasionally. Changes will be posted here with a revised date.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions? Open an issue on <a href="https://github.com/a5ah1/ffmpeg-party/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">the GitHub repository</a>.</p>
